@alliw98 And yes it is a Pirated copy, because Dead Space 3 is not made for Mac.
It is made for Xbox 360, Ps3, and PC. That means someone had to convert it from a PC game to a Mac to make it playable.
Therefore, it is Pirated.

@naffbilly Like what happened with me, you're computer probably deleted the file "deadspace3.exe" because there was a virus in it.

"deadspace3.exe" is the actual game file. Without that, you cannot play the game.

Try disabling your Anti-Virus, and then unzipping the file again. Should work =)
